I"
<p>记录用ssh工具XShell连接谷歌云服务器。</p>

<p>● <a href="https://blog.csdn.net/datadev_sh/article/details/79593360" title="https://blog.csdn.net/datadev_sh/article/details/79593360" target="_blank">datadev_sh博客原贴</a></p>

<h1 id="1登录google服务器">1.登录google服务器</h1>

<p><img src="http://walidream.com:9999/blogImage/server/server_1.png" alt="ssl" /></p>

<h3 id="切换到root角色">切换到root角色</h3>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>sudo -i
</code></pre></div></div>

<h3 id="修改ssh配置文件etcsshsshd_config">修改SSH配置文件/etc/ssh/sshd_config</h3>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>vi /etc/ssh/sshd_config
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>修改PermitRootLogin和PasswordAuthentication为yes</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code># Authentication:
PermitRootLogin yes //默认为no，需要开启root用户访问改为yes

# Change to no to disable tunnelled clear text passwords
PasswordAuthentication yes //默认为no，改为yes开启密码登陆
</code></pre></div></div>

<h3 id="给root用户设置密码">给root用户设置密码</h3>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>passwd root  #设置root密码后直接可以用root账户登录
</code></pre></div></div>

<h3 id="重启ssh服务使修改生效">重启SSH服务使修改生效</h3>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>/etc/init.d/ssh restart
</code></pre></div></div>

